data.description: Excellent opportunity to own a two-bedroom ,two bath villa in the Villages of Woodlake - The Cloisters. Large side and rear yard. The community is secluded.  Shopping, restaurants and entertainment are at a convenient distance from the property.  55+ requires that at least one occupant of the residence is 55.  Beautiful lakes throughout the community. Amenities include pool, clubhouse, tennis courts, shuffleboard.  New air conditioning, water heater, garbage disposal October 2023!
